{"tid":1292613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日喺香港嘅支那人 你大鑊了","createTime":"2019-07-07T11:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T12:12:06.000Z","uid":165782,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b707f488b78cae77f24b147daad4e4aeb981890c","tid":1292613,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"你班支那豬扮唔知都無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估你話唔知你個黨會信你咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢哋玩有罪推定，除非你挖咗自己個腦（如有）出嚟俾佢哋睇 佢哋先會考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係 國安即日上門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寧枉勿縱嘅支那法律係唔係好正呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家見到我個post係咪即刻明曬我哋點解反送中呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算你真係唔知我哋遊行係為乜野事 共產黨都唔會信你 因為一放錯一個俾佢周街講周街唱咁佢封鎖咗成個月嘅努力咪白費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一路好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c741d909d3a4c8b2ae69d60715fb2c2c58eaf9","tid":1292613,"uid":165782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:43:18.000Z","msg":"翻牆出嚟搗亂個批五毛三毛一毛 你哋都睇路喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14354e3b36e12a954e3ab26c2c203e4b9ec4f5ab","tid":1292613,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"你們知道得太多了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db0fdd65975ded1a1c75b453a2def3be360bc1f","tid":1292613,"uid":165782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:07:47.000Z","msg":"有招教你 就係先發制人<br />\n喺支那當眼處大鑼大鼓宣揚自由 等你多啲同鄉見到 還掂廣東武漢都有示威 唔差在34個省都一齊嚟 夠人多佢咪唔得閒搵你囉 還掂佢家下同侵打緊貿易戰 你哋內外夾攻咪可以保命囉<br />\n做人做鬼睇今次 等到國安上門就無救喇"},{"pid":"6d244b3a156806c67088c25e471b8a7a28e6808b","tid":1292613,"uid":44031,"like":6,"dislike"